&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;h2 id="conclusion"&gt;Conclusion&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;AI coding tools are revolutionizing the way developers write and manage code. By integrating tools like GitHub &lt;a href="https://github.com/features/copilot?ref=AFFILIATE_ID"&gt;Copilot&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://www.tabnine.com/?ref=AFFILIATE_ID"&gt;Tabnine&lt;/a&gt;, Kite, or OpenAI’s Codex into your workflow, you can enhance your productivity, improve code quality, and streamline your projects.&lt;/p&gt;
