&lt;li&gt;Excellent for collaborative projects.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Offers real-time code suggestions and debugging help.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;User-friendly interface for beginners and experts alike.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cons&lt;/strong&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;
